{"type": "article", "id": 4656, "title": "Molecula 分子灯", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-24T07:32:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052334326bTnUfaZmvyidNMG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t阿根廷设计师 Benjamin Migliore 日前推出一款名为「Molecula Lamp」的灯具，既可以用作墙灯，也可以用作台灯。立体几何形的外观使得这款灯看上去像是一个轮廓清晰的雕塑，呈带有圆滑交接点的有机结构。Benjamin Migliore 将 LED 灯带隐藏在几何结构的线条之中，形成混合的立体光源。白天不需要开灯时，Molecula Lamp 则可以扮演一件装置雕塑的角色。如需购买，请联系 design@benjaminmigliore.com。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052334296eCBisG24trzMwqc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233430Jqp8absZLzAKhkPQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233430NJB9aUuRr10tI6Zk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233431INRxvCWe7tShHykM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}